Successful processing of Billing Details will result in a confirmation screen stating the successful processing of billing information for the
company. The user can view the details which have been processed or select Done CTA to return to where the flow initially started.

If the back office user selects the Decline CTA on the Company Billing Details Overlay, the Decline Billing Information flow is triggered. This is
the initial page where additional comments can be inputted by the back office approver which can be seen by the front office when viewing a
company profile. Details such as why the billing details are declined are expected to be inputted in here, and any necessary changes that must
be made by the front office user.
